  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Current devp2p connections are not rate limited. This might be important for home users and especially important for mobile devices. We want to prevent les/whisper from accidentally eating all available mobile traffic.\r\n\r\nI am considering to wrap all connections that are created in p2p.Server with a single token based rate limiter. And allow to reconfigure this rate limiter without p2p.Server restart. \r\n\r\n@fjl what do you think about it?\r\n\r\ncc @ligi as you are building mobile wallet with LES",
